#Approach:

💡 IDEA
- Circular array me answer 2 jagah se aa sakta hai:

1. Normal Subarray
   → Standard Kadane (maxSum)

2. Circular Subarray
   → Middle ka minimum sum part hata do.
   → Remaining prefix + suffix milkar max circular sum bana denge.

Formula:

Circular Sum =
Total Sum - Minimum Subarray Sum

Final Answer =
max(maxSum, total - minSum)

⚙️ APPROACH
1. Kadane laga kar maximum subarray sum nikalo.
   → maxSum

2. Reverse Kadane (Min Kadane) laga kar minimum subarray sum nikalo.
   → minSum

3. Total array sum calculate karo.
   → total

4. Circular answer:
   total - minSum

5. Return:
   max(maxSum, total - minSum)

6. Edge Case:
   Agar saare elements negative hain,
   toh circular formula 0 de dega (wrong).
   Isliye directly maxSum return karo.

📝 EXAMPLE 1

nums = [5,-3,5]

Normal Kadane:

maxSum = 7
[5,-3,5]

----------------

Total Sum:

total = 7

----------------

Minimum Subarray:

[-3]

minSum = -3

----------------

Circular Sum:

7 - (-3)
= 10

Answer:

max(7,10)
= 10

Subarray:

[5] + [5]
(wrap around)

------------------------------------------------

📝 EXAMPLE 2

nums = [1,-2,3,-2]

maxSum = 3

total = 0

minSum = -2

Circular Sum

0 - (-2)
= 2

Answer

max(3,2)
= 3

❓ WHY TOTAL - MINSUM WORKS

Circular subarray:

[5,-3,5]

Instead of finding what to take,

Think:
"What should I remove?"

Remove:
[-3]

Remaining:

[5] + [5]

Sum = 10

That's exactly:

Total - MinSubarray

⏱️ COMPLEXITY
Time  : O(N)

- Max Kadane = O(N)
- Min Kadane = O(N)
- Total Sum = O(N)

Space : O(1)

🎯 INTERVIEW POINT
- Circular answer = Total Sum - Minimum Subarray Sum.
- Problem ko "maximum choose karna" nahi,
  "minimum remove karna" socho.
- Most important edge case:

  All Negative Array

Example:

[-3,-2,-5]

maxSum = -2
minSum = -10
total = -10

total - minSum = 0 ❌

Empty subarray ban jaayega.

Isliye:

if(maxSum < 0)
    return maxSum;

- Standard Kadane + Min Kadane = Complete Solution.

#Code:

public class Solution {

    private int MaxKadane(int[] arr){
      int sum = 0;
      int maxi = Integer.MIN_VALUE;

      for(int i=0; i<arr.length; i++){
        sum += arr[i];
        if(sum > maxi){
          maxi = sum;
        }
        if(sum < 0){
          sum = 0;
        }
      }
      return maxi;
    }

    private int MinKadane(int[] arr){
      int sum = 0;
      int mini = Integer.MAX_VALUE;

      for(int i=0; i<arr.length; i++){
        sum += arr[i];
        if(sum < mini){
          mini = sum;
        }
        if(sum > 0){
          sum = 0;
        }
      }
      return mini;
    }

    public int maxSubarraySumCircular(int[] a) {
      //You can code here
      int maxSum = MaxKadane(a);
      int minSum = MinKadane(a);

      int total = 0;

      for(int i=0; i<a.length; i++){
        total += a[i];
      }

      //edge case
      if(maxSum < 0){
        return maxSum;
      }

      return Math.max(maxSum, total - minSum);
      
    }
}
